COMMENTS="Optional :
			- projectM plugin depends on projectM, and qt-4.x-opengl
			- mplayer plugin depends on any mplayer extension available
			- jack plugin depends on jack
			- sound output plugins depend on alsa, oss or pulseaudio

		Qmmp supports Winamp and Xmms skins:
			winamp 5: http://gnome-look.org/content/show.php?content=14870
			xmms seamaster: http://www.kde-look.org/content/show.php?content=31224
		To change skin settings->appearance->add and choose skin file (you don't need to extract compressed files)"

